<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ de ēn diǎn zú gòu wǒ yòng 迦南849</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ de ēn diǎn zú gòu wǒ yòng, zhǔ de ēn diǎn zú gòu wǒ yòng.
 màn màn zhǎng lù yōu yōu suì yuè, zhǔ de ēn diǎn zú gòu zú gòu wǒ yòng.
 duō shǎo gè wú zhù de shí hòu, duō shǎo gè wēi jí guān kǒu, shì zhǔ shēn chū tā yuán zhù de shuāng shǒu.
 yǒng yuǎn bù huì fǒu rèn, tiān tiān dōu jì zhù, zhǔ de ēn diǎn zú gòu zú gòu wǒ yòng.
 a a a a</lyrics>
